The Genererator Caucus will hold a conference call on Tuesday, November 13th at 11:00 a.m. (EST) to prepare for the generator interconnection meetings next week.  To access the call, dial 1-800-937-6563 and ask for the Julie Simon/EPSA call.  The agenda for next week is tenatively scheduled to include queuing issues on Wednesday and interconnection procedures on Thursday.

Also, attached are the consensus points developed from today's generator caucus on rights associated with interconnection services and the studies need to complete those services.

